        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Roadmap</h1>
            <p class="govuk-body">Here’s a list of the new functionality we’re planning to offer through GOV.UK&nbsp;Pay.</p>
            <div class="govuk-inset-text">
              <p class="govuk-body">This roadmap is only a guide and may change. We work in 3-monthly cycles.</p>
            </div>
             <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Recently released</h2>
              <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                 <li>Make it easier to reconcile transactions by using metadata</li> 
                 <li>Prepopulate transaction details</li>  
                 <li>Support for <a class="govuk-link" href="https://docs.payments.service.gov.uk/optional_features/digital_wallets/#digital-wallets">Apple Pay and Google Pay</a></li>
                 <li>Apply custom branding to <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.payments.service.gov.uk/payment-links/">payment links</a></li> 
                 <li>Payment links in Welsh</li> 
                 <li>Return Provider ID in API searches</li> 
                 <li>Launch Direct Debit service</li>
               </ul>
      
             <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">July to September 2019</h2>
              
             <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">In progress</h3>
              <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                 <li>Support for 3D Secure 2.0</li>
                 <li>Reporting for telephone payments</li>
                 <li>Return card type (debit/ credit) in API searches</li>
               </ul>
      
             <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">October to December 2019</h2>
              <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                 <li>Transaction reporting across multiple services</li>
                 <li>Payout reporting for services using GOV.UK Pay's <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.payments.service.gov.uk/payment-service-provider/">Payment Service Provider</a></li> 
                 <li>Support for Apple Pay and Google Pay for services using GOV.UK Pay's PSP</li>
               </ul>
      
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Later</h2>
              <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                <li>Recurring card payments</li>
                <li>Scheduled Direct Debit</li>
                <li>Telephone payments</li>
                <li>Chip and pin payments</li>
              </ul>
     
